            "title": "美國將對重型卡車和廚櫃徵收關稅 10月1日起實施",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國將對重型卡車和廚櫃徵收關稅 10月1日起實施\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aGim_ivWQce8M5Ylytg3fg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/afeb21c0-8a29-11f0-bfff-8c624e04368f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國將對重型卡車和廚櫃徵收關稅 10月1日起實施</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
